<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates>
We are investigating increased error rates and latencies for the AWS Management Console in the EU-WEST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates>
Between 5:03 AM and 5:53 AM PST we experienced increased error rates and latencies for the AWS Management Console in the EU-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
